OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly sunny spells in the east
OL,6,Fturn cloudier with heavy rain
OL,7,Fspreading north and east. Rain
OL,8,Fpersistenting in the west, which can
OL,9,Fbe heavy in places. Sunny spells
OL,10,Freturn to Northern Ireland later.
OL,11,FTemperatures just above the seasonal
OL,12,Faverage.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain moving eastwards, heavy
OL,15,Fat times, especially southeast by the
OL,16,Fmorning. Showers developing in the
OL,17,Fwest with the risk of thunder. Low
OL,18,Fcloud and coastal fog further north.
OL,19,FMild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
