OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FHeavy showers and thunder
OL,6,Facross the south and east, where it
OL,7,Fcan be gusty. Drier spells developing
OL,8,Fin the west later with some sunnier
OL,9,Fspells. Temperatures around average
OL,10,Ffor June.
